Extreme Copy Pro 2.3.4 description :-

Here are some key features of "ExtremeCopy Pro":

    Controlable. You can pause/resume copy process when you need.
    Simple. The operation of copy/move files as simple as Windows default copying, you no need do anything once you installed ExtremeCopy which will replace Windows copying function as default, or change this default setting when you need. User Interface looks simple and friendly.
    Multiple Languages. Support multiple country languages of file name in order to keep original language text of file name


What's New in This Release: 

   1) Fixed 'Replace Dialog' UI problem
   2) Fixed couple of crash bugs.
   3) Fixed Duplicate installation info in Control Panel after upgraded.
   4) Fixed switch '-task_file' bug in command line.
   5) Fixed shut down option for task queue.
   6) Updated crash report sending.
